<p>I actually assumed this was a person that was unseen, unheard, unknown. People would think that the ROOM was an anomaly, not the person. They would guard the ROOM, but no the person.<br />
I can't rightly explain the whole infection part&#8230;unless that is some headcannon I haven't seen yet.</p>

