			<div class="content" id="post-content-2825005">
									

<p>I think the infection thing was just supposed to be this guy's assumption. It doesn't seem like he really knows what's going on, other than that he's being held in some kind of facility, other people are being held there too, and it doesn't seem like a typical prison. He may have even overheard researchers talking about doing tests.Quarantine seems like a reasonable conclusion, even though we know it's wrong.</p>

